<p>(v) reinstate the final environmental impact statement entitled "Final Environmental Impact Statement for the Coastal Plain Oil and Gas Leasing Program," which is referred to in "Notice of Availability," 84 Fed. Reg. 50472 (September 25, 2019);</p>
